> <b><span style="color: #FFD700 ; font-size: 1.5rem;">*Online trading academy*</span></b>

**Online Trading Academy allows prospective students to sample the program via free courses before committing to its fee-based training. Online share trading involves buying and selling stocks through an online platform. Using the online share trading account, you can easily buy or sell share stocks, mutual funds, bonds, and other securities without the need for an intermediate broker or agent. It also allows interested individuals to sample the program via free courses before deciding to commit to its fee-based courses. Additionally, the organization boasts an extensive list of more than 100 dedicated instructors with real-world trading experience.**

